{"tha-ap444:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap444:0.2":"Vibhitakavagga ","tha-ap444:0.3":"Koladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap444:1.1":"“Ajinena nivatthoham, ","tha-ap444:1.2":"Vakaciradharo tada; ","tha-ap444:1.3":"Khariya purayitvana, ","tha-ap444:1.4":"Kolamhasim mamassamam. ","tha-ap444:2.1":"Tamhi kale sikhi buddho, ","tha-ap444:2.2":"eko adutiyo ahu; ","tha-ap444:2.3":"Mamassamam upagacchi, ","tha-ap444:2.4":"jananto sabbakalikam. ","tha-ap444:3.1":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap444:3.2":"vanditvana ca subbatam; ","tha-ap444:3.3":"Ubho hatthehi paggayha, ","tha-ap444:3.4":"kolam buddhassadasaham. ","tha-ap444:4.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap444:4.2":"yam phalamadadim tada; ","tha-ap444:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap444:4.4":"koladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap444:5.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap444:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap444:5.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap444:6.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap444:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap444:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap444:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap444:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap444:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap444:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma koladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap444:9.1":"Koladayakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}